    "ResUNetResUNet is one of the UNet-based segmentation models based on residual architecture.",
    "ResUNet is a model developed to overcome the difficulties arising from training deep neural networks.",
    "One of the difficulties in the mentioned training is that deep learning-based segmentation models consist of too many layers.",
    "A large number of layers usually forces the system to memorize.",
    "As a result, system performance decreases."
